title: Heroes of Might and Magic IV + 2 Expansions
description:
Heroes of Might and Magic IV

Expansions:
The Gathering Storm
Winds of War

Install:

1. Extract the RAR&#039;s 

2. Start the autorun.exe and press the UK-flag (it will only work to install the game in English).

3. Press one of the logos to install that game (start with installing the main game, after that it doesn&#039;t matter which expansion you install first).

4.Just start the game and enjoy!

PS. You do NOT need any crack or serial number.

Sorry if I have miss spelled something.
